  # 社交互动设计

  This is a code bundle for 社交互动设计. The original project is available at https://www.figma.com/design/FlygnHEsIDAl3dJJdUTlHG/%E7%A4%BE%E4%BA%A4%E4%BA%92%E5%8A%A8%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1.

  ## Running the code

  Run `npm i` to install the dependencies.

  Run `npm run dev` to start the development server.
